Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:24.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:29.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}In springtime I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:35.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}Then skipping along，oh I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:40.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}I looked at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:45.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:50.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}I danced with the peanut butterflies
